Class TGJsonRequest<T extends TGResponse>

  • java.lang.Object

  • Type Parameters:
    T - TGResponse
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<com.android.volley.Request<T>>

    public abstract class TGJsonRequest<T extends TGResponse>
extends TGRequest<T>
    TGJsonRequest has been created by extending TGRequest which internally uses Volley framework. TGJsonRequest encapsulates network calls and conversion of json response to custom T object. It internally uses GSon library for converting string into Java objects. It supports SerializedName expression to map Json element name to java object's attribute name.
